KitKat/GoldenEye

KitKat::
Leaking mech fluid from her neck to her ankles, she stood there with 
her rifle in her hands.  She fired on the maximals with everything 
she had.  She fired at Deemos, the chosen ones, stronghold.  She 
fired grenades at the Chosen ones.  She took a step back and kept 
firing.


GoldenEye:
She flew up into the air and waited for a bot to step forward.  She 
swooped down and readied her talons to Blender's head and neck.
